      <title>2月，全球中国EV出口到全球18％y/y至92,625</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-ev-exports-worldwide-fall-18-y-y-to-92-625-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据中国习俗的数据，2月中国对比利时的EV出口量下降了41％至10,105，这是所有国家或地区中最大的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-ev-exports-worldwide-fall-18-y-y-to-92-625-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度科技初创公司价值1000亿美元，目前正在寻求IPO到2027年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/india-tech-startups-worth-100-billion-seen-seeking-ipos-by-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据该国一位互联网公司的顶级交易顾问之一的说，到2027年，超过三十家具有1000亿美元估值的技术初创公司将公开公开，这将标志着印度的股票销售反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/india-tech-startups-worth-100-billion-seen-seeking-ipos-by-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 06:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国吹捧贸易福利在最后一条关税上诉中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-touts-trade-benefits-for-us-in-last-ditch-tariff-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国强调了美国的农民和科技公司在执政的共产党的官方报纸上是经济关系的受益者，这显然吸引了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）预计宣布新的全球关税的前夕，呼吁较大的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-touts-trade-benefits-for-us-in-last-ditch-tariff-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>什么是筹码法？特朗普为什么要改变它？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/what-is-the-us-chips-act-how-does-trump-want-to-change-it-as-he-eyes-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战争以及将制造业带回美国的努力使他的前任签名成就之一：《筹码与科学法》。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/what-is-the-us-chips-act-how-does-trump-want-to-change-it-as-he-eyes-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 04:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国正试图打击社会骗局。美国不是那么多。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-04-02/the-uk-is-trying-to-fight-social-scams-the-us-not-so-much</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将到来的英国法律提供了有关如何获取网络和消息传递应用程序来捍卫欺诈的测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-04-02/the-uk-is-trying-to-fight-social-scams-the-us-not-so-much</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
